        "setup": "Sign up or log in to your Fugle account from [Fugle Developer Docs](https://developer.fugle.tw/), then go to [金鑰申請及管理](https://developer.fugle.tw/docs/key/) to apply for and manage your market data API key. The docs state market data authentication uses the `X-API-KEY` header and the site links this page as the key application flow.",
